You don’t need to farm 50+ projects

Here are the main ones you should focus on:

@Polymarket
There are many prediction markets, but none will compare to $POLY

Instead of splitting volume across platforms, just use Polymarket

Team already confirmed the airdrop

@AbstractChain
PENGU Airdrop was one of the biggest on Solana

I think the same could happen with Abstract since it’s their biggest marketing play, and not many people farm it properly yet

@bulktrade
Top-tier perps farm after the Backpack launch, I would focus there for now (currently only testnet)

@xplaceapp
Only for Seeker users team confirmed 2.5% of token allocation, still very early, and token planned for Q4 this year

@Gradient_HQ
One of the free airdrops that could make you a few thousand dollars
Team building for a long time could be something big

@onrefinance
Still early and one of the best products to earn yield on USDC
Generating 10% from insurance deals, already $120M+ AUM

@xeetodai
Since InfoFi is slowing down, people are using earned Xeets for creator packs. If you have Xeets, use them to open packs and get creator cards.

@piggybank_fi
New protocol on Solana with vault strategies and APYs you don’t see elsewhere

Caps fill quickly, so follow them and enable notifications to catch deposits

@Arcium
No confirmation of a token yet, but I believe they may reward users of apps built on their privacy layer, umbra is the first app worth using

Just 9 projects, all with big narratives

Perps, Neobanks, AI, Prediction markets, DeFi Yield, Depin, Privacy

